onal efficiency and reducing costs associated with security incidents. This certification is not just a box to check\u2014it\u2019s a continuous commitment to excellence and security.\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Amid growing security threats, Tech Quarter\u2019s certification highlights its commitment to proactive cybersecurity and data protection.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tech Quarter, a growing software development provider, has officially obtained the ISO 27001 certification, reinforcing its commitment to the highest standards of information security. This globally recognized certification demonstrates the company\u2019s dedication to protecting client data and ensuring secure software solutions. Understanding ISO 27001 ISO 27001 is the world&#8217;s most recognized standard for information security [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5079,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[67,155,40,6],"class_list":["post-5075","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-business","tag-cybersecurity","tag-software-development","tag-software-programming","tag-Tech Chicago"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Tech Chicago Achieves ISO 27001 Certification - Tech Chicago<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Tech Quarter achieves ISO 27001 certification, reinforcing its commitment to information security and secure software solutions.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/Tech Chicago.io\/Tech Chicago-achieves-iso-27001-certification\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" 